<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="worst-adj">worst <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /wɜːst/    美 /wɜːrst/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>最坏的；最差的；病情严重的；最恶劣的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It was by far the worst speech he had ever made.
这是迄今为止他发表的最糟糕的演讲。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>This is the worst accident for years.
这么多年来最严重的一次事故。</p></div></div>